Message Should Be In The Form:

<std_msgs::msg::String>
"CMD@trackpath/trackname.format@startingtime"

CMD can be:
	"New" - It loads the new passed track, resetting the previous one.
	"Pause" - It pauses the execution of the current track. Trackpath can be omitted.
	"Play" - It resumes the execution of the current track. Trackpath can be omitted.
	"Stop" - It blocks the execution of the current track. Trackpath can be omitted.
